{"tid":1537060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"最近既勇武行動有啲頹","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T20:23:10.000Z","uid":289253,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0df659d5513bc955dd501f46a7bcde258304ac11","tid":1537060,"uid":289253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"我記得對上一次最有氣勢既勇武已經係元朗7.27，剩係戰鼓聲已經嚇窒班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實一直以黎我覺得和理非係好有作為，點解唔做多啲<br />\n特別係「軟實力」（對唔住我詞窮），唔係和理非既合作，我地唔會有國際戰線，唔會屌柒啲藍絲盲閪屌得咁口響<br />\n但係每一次上陣，有哨兵話防暴出現，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非永遠都排晒長龍落去搭黨鐵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實衰啲講一句，死既傷既都係勇武，子彈都係勇武擋，比人拉既都係勇武以身相救，現場仲有乜野好怕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果和理非係怕催淚彈，我最多咪索多兩啖，用個肺幫你地過濾<br />\n我只係希望和理非可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">留多一陣</span></span>，係後排做返個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣勢</span></span>，嗌返兩句光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命，最好就梗係嗌埋前線勇武加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一黎有班靚仔靚女嗌兩聲真係會士氣大增<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，二黎人數就係勇武最佳既防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而且勇武唔洗再隔住個豬嘴大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba591d55c3e80d14e08d85af3dd72fb6fbea348","tid":1537060,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:41:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\